// Windows - Codechef
#include <stdio.h>
#include <stdlib.h>

int main(int argc, char *argv[])
{
  int cases,flx,fly,frx,fry,slx,sly,srx,sry;
  scanf("%d",&cases);
  while(cases--)
  {
                scanf("%d%d%d%d%d%d%d%d",&flx,&fly,&frx,&fry,&slx,&sly,&srx,&sry);
                if((slx<=frx)&&(sly<=fry)) printf("%d %d %d %d\n",slx,fly,frx,sry);
                else printf("No Overlap\n");
                }
  //system("PAUSE");	
  return 0;
}
